{
  "stem": "521.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Actually, I could have seen him other times, because he was sleeping.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the time was limited to Sunday, when he then came home to eat lunch at 12:30, until 1 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And after he spent another hour to have a conversation with me-- which I really appreciated.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But he was a good man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was providing everything what we needed, what my mother needed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we cannot complain that we were neglected, financially.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Emanuel, and he came from a family of eight, I guess.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My grandfather was born in 1848-- he lived until 1937, and he died at the age of 89.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My-- my-- my grandfather was born, also, in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So was his father.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "His father's name was [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Pinkus, ?] and [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Pinkus, ?] his grandfather was called Gabriel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now Gabriel, at the turn of the last century-- not 1700 to 1800, was a very curious name for-- for a Jew.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They came to Hungary because they were living in Moravia.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Moravia is a part of the Czech Republ-- Republic, and the capital is [?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Brn, ?] or Brno.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the reason they left Moravia is because the Jews had no right to marry.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Only the oldest son could marry in Moravia, and the rest of the boys couldn't get married, which wasn't very good because most people want to get married and establish a family.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But the Moravians didn't want the Jews to-- to-- to have too many children, because too many Jews were no good in-- at that time, as it is no good in most of the countries today.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So they were limited, and they came to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Hungary-- now it was the same country, it was a Austro-Hungarian-- Austro-Hungarian country of the combination of Hungary and Austria.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
